### Getting Started:-
- You must have NPM (8.11.0) and Node (v16.16.0) installed to run the app.
- To install everything in every package run the command `npm install` from your terminal in the root directory.
- Then, you can run the platform for development purposes by running `npm run start` in the same directory.


### General Tech Stack/Tools List:-

  - Nodejs
  - JavaSript
  - Mongoose
  - Express

- Other
  - Github
  - Git
  - NPM
  - Open source libraries


### Postman collection:-

##For creating User:-

  mutation createUser($params: UserInput){
createUser(params:$params){
    email
	    firstName
	    lastName
      email
    }
}

##For Login User:-

mutation userLogin($email: String!, $password: String!){
    userLogin(email: $email, password: $password){
       message,
       token
    }
}

##For Creating Organisation:-

mutation createOrg($params: OrganizationInput){
        createOrg(params:$params){
            email,
            name,
            ownerName
      }
}
